  "details": "A security flaw has been discovered in Edimax BR-6428NS 1.10. This affects the function formWirelessTbl of the file /goform/formWirelessTbl of the component POST Request Handler. Performing a manipulation of the argument vapurl results in buffer overflow. The attack can be initiated remotely. The exploit has been released to the public and may be used for attacks. The vendor was contacted early about this disclosure but did not respond in any way.",
